title: United Kingdom Imports of Salt Sulphur Earths & Stone
description: Imports of Salt, Sulphur, Earths & Stone in the United Kingdom decreased to 94.91 GBP Million in September from 105.47 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Salt, Sulphur, Earths & Stone in the United Kingdom averaged 50.57 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 118.84 GBP Million in May of 2022 and a record low of 23.10 GBP Million in February of 2002. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Salt, Sulphur, Earths & Stone.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
